title: Sans with odd y and w
content:
Hi,

Someone sent me this for an ID and I have run out of ideas. I thought it looked familiar, but I can't place it. The y and w are quite distinctive, and even the D seems a bit oddly shaped. In some respects it looks a bit like a customized Optima, but what do you all think?

Thanks,  
- Mike
